{"tid":548623,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[高級放題]到底碗屋係唔係真係咁正？","createTime":"2018-02-02T18:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T10:36:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":64,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"c835ccc27deb29ca9f180953dfe36f9e53f4ca08","tid":548623,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T18:07:15.000Z","msg":"成日食放題 <br />\n我既放題之路都由深水埗去到長沙灣再去到旺角再去到尖沙咀 <br />\n雖然食過既放題都多 <br />\n但價錢同質素其實大多數都分別不大 <br />\n(兆萬果d劣到不能再劣就唔好提) <br />\n平則都要百幾 <br />\n貴則都只係二百幾三百 <br />\n<br />\n但我上網見到中環碗屋 <br />\n計埋加一要成六百蚊位 <br />\n睇相又唔覺得有咩咁特別 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問下咁多位食過既巴打 <br />\n到底值唔值得一試 <br />\n同埋你覺得正既位係邊"},{"pid":"b902b7169a52f80cdd125e925866827435f42fac","tid":548623,"uid":72608,"like":110,"dislike":2,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T18:47:59.000Z","msg":"1次碗屋=4次下級放題,打邊爐,雞煲=3次中級放題=2次中上價放題=1次自助餐<br />\n<br />\n所以我窮,未食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1bde5be58093d38030f2bee153d920f3e053a3","tid":548623,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T20:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6831580b90f44c9bb29b90c22b087205c32ec9db","tid":548623,"uid":6562,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T01:09:13.000Z","msg":"好耐以前食過幾正 而家唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e772cee9c51b08ba228021491a47811af39ac239","tid":548623,"uid":22762,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"係有心機同高質啲嘅野食<br />\n瘋狂食鱈魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲寸燒 全部都好味<br />\n食用大乜屋個啲係濕鳩放題 <br />\n碗屋會係日本餐廳質素 但任食<br />\n<br />\n不過近年都差左 特別係搬左去L Place<br />\n<br />\n利申: 食左廿年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我